          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780140046960" href="/book/show/1886949.The_End_of_the_Affair">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/10752235-l-a-i-n-e-y-back-in-a-bit?shelf=marvelous-writing">marvelous-writing</a>, 
